if you ask students

00:29:44.489 --> 00:29:46.030
what they thought
about the clickers,

00:29:46.030 --> 00:29:49.360
they were not at all resentful
of the use of clickers.

00:29:49.360 --> 00:29:51.940
And they did not see them as a
way of just taking attendance.

00:29:51.940 --> 00:29:56.230
They didn't think they were
sort of baby or whatever.

00:29:56.230 --> 00:29:59.930
And they were therefore
more effective.

