00:31:07.820 --> 00:31:10.460
not innovative, maybe
not groundbreaking,

00:31:10.460 --> 00:31:13.280
but a solid pedagogical use.

00:31:13.280 --> 00:31:15.620
For others, if you're going
to use them effectively

00:31:15.620 --> 00:31:17.203
in the classroom,
you're going to have

00:31:17.203 --> 00:31:19.610
to spend some time engaging
with the technology,

00:31:19.610 --> 00:31:22.070
making sure you understand
it, making sure you understand

00:31:22.070 --> 00:31:24.530
